      </p>
      <pre>public int MoreThanHalfNum_Solution(int[] nums) {
    int majority = nums[0];
    for (int i = 1, cnt = 1; i &lt; nums.length; i++) {
        cnt = nums[i] == majority ? cnt + 1 : cnt - 1;
        if (cnt == 0) {
            majority = nums[i];
            cnt = 1;
        }
    }
    int cnt = 0;
    for (int val : nums)
        if (val == majority)
            cnt++;
    return cnt &gt; nums.length / 2 ? majority : 0;
}</pre>
