    <pre><code class="language-plaintext">Input: S = &quot;ababcbacadefegdehijhklij&quot;
Output: [9,7,8]
Explanation:
The partition is &quot;ababcbaca&quot;, &quot;defegde&quot;, &quot;hijhklij&quot;.
